<html><head><style type="text/css">body {font-size:13px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color:#000;}ul {margin-bottom:0;}#content {margin:0 auto;width:990px;overflow:hidden;}#content, table.output, table.output table {font-size:13px;font-weight: normal !important;line-height: 1.85px;}table.output tr th {font-weight: bold;font-size:13px;}table.output tr td span {}table.output tr td.border {border-top:1px solid #000;}table.output tr td.border-bottom {border-bottom:1px solid #000;}h1 { font-size:16px;}p.topTxt {font-size: 13px; text-align: center; font-weight:bold;}span.red, span.red-area, .red-area {color:red;}</style><title>Voicemail Script - Business Value Focus (Long)</title>
