<body>
<div id="content">
		<h1 align="center">Voicemail Script &#45; Business Value Focus (Long)</h1>
	<p class="topTxt"  >
		Scripter Pro (sample)  for 
		sales managers	</p>
	
	<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="output">
		<tr><td class="border">&nbsp;</td></tr>
		<tr>
			<td>
				
		        <p>Hello <span class="red-area">[Prospect First Name]</span>
				
				   this is [Your name] from My Company (sample).
				
				</p>
		        <p>Purpose for my call is that we help  
					sales managers to 
				</p>
				<p> <span class="red-area">(Pick three from below) </span>

					<ul>
												<li>
								improve the amount of sales that new sales hires generate							</li>
													<li>
								decrease the amount of time and cost needed to train and get new sales people up and running							</li>
													<li>
								improve the lead generation of the entire sales team							</li>
													<li>
								decrease the sales staff turnover and all cost that come with that							</li>
													<li>
								get more sales performance out of their under-performing staff							</li>
													<li>
								decrease the amount of time and cost required to train sales resources 							</li>
										</ul>
				
				</p>
				
				 
				
		        <p><span class="red-area">(Optional disqualify statement) </span>I actually do not know if you are a fit for what we do and that is why I was calling you with a question or two.</p>
				<p>
					I will try you again next week. If you would like to reach me in the meantime, my number is [Your phone].
				</p>
				<p>Again, this is [Your name] calling from My Company (sample), [Your phone].</p>
				
				<p>Thank you and I look forward to talking with you soon.</p>
		        
			</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
</div>	
